#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transactions and Splits"
msgstr "Tehingud ja alltehingud"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balanced transactions"
msgstr "Bilansseeritud tehingud"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As with GnuCash, data is entered in the form of transactions, each "
#| "generally consisting of 2 or more split entries. In fact, valid GnuCash "
#| "transactions will always contain at least 2 splits, and to conform to "
#| "GnuCash's double-entry bookkeeping standard, these must be in monetary "
#| "balance (i.e., they must balance out to zero). &kappname; encourages, but "
#| "does not enforce, this standard, but any imported transaction which is "
#| "not balanced will be marked in the ledger view as having a problem."
msgid ""
"In both programs, data is entered in the form of transactions, each "
"generally consisting of 2 or more split entries. In fact, valid &gnucash; "
"transactions will always contain at least 2 splits, and to conform to "
"&gnucash;'s double-entry bookkeeping standard, these must be in monetary "
"balance (&ie;, they must balance out to zero). &kmymoney; encourages, but "
"does not enforce, this standard, but any imported transaction which is not "
"balanced will be marked in the Ledgers View as having a problem."
msgstr ""
"Nagu GnuCashis koosnevad tehingutena sisestatud andmed tavaliselt kahest või "
"enamast tükeldatud kirjest. Õieti sisaldab korrektne GnuCashi tehing alati "
"vähemalt kaks alltehingut ning GnuCashi kahekordse kirjendamise standardile "
"vastamiseks peavad need olema rahaliselt tasakaalus (s.t. bilanss peab olema "
"null). &kappname; toetab, aga mitte ei sunni seda standardit peale, kuid "
"kõik imporditud tehingud, mis ei ole bilansseeritud, märgitakse "
"pearaamatuvaates probleemseks."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payees"
msgstr "Maksesaajad"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; prefers that all transactions have a Payee (a generic term "
#| "that encompasses both payees and payers), and unlike GnuCash, a list of "
#| "these payees is maintained. Payee names are generated by the importer "
#| "from the GnuCash transaction's Description field."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; prefers that all transactions have a Payee (a generic term that "
"encompasses both payees and payers,) and unlike &gnucash;, it maintains a "
"list of these payees. Payee names are generated by the importer from the "
"&gnucash; transaction's Description field."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; eelistab, et igal tehingul oleks maksesaaja (see on üldine "
"mõiste, mis hõlmab nii maksesaajat kui ka maksjat), ja erinevalt GnuCashist "
"hoitakse ka maksesaajate loend alal. Maksesaajate nimed genereerib importija "
"GnuCashi tehingute välja Description põhjal."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfers"
msgstr "Ülekanded"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:200
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; uses the term Transfer to describe a transaction which does "
#| "not involve a Category, but only transfers money between Asset and/or "
#| "Liability accounts."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; uses the term Transfer to describe a transaction which does not "
"involve a Category, but only transfers money between Asset and/or Liability "
"accounts."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; kasutab mõistet \"ülekanne\" tehingute kohta, millel pole "
"kategooriat, vaid mis ainult kannab raha üle vara- ja/või kohustiskonto "
"vahel."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconcile"
msgstr "Kooskõlastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:208
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; provides an account reconciliation function similar to that of "
#| "GnuCash, and the corresponding transaction status will be imported."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides an account reconciliation function similar to that of "
"&gnucash;, and the corresponding transaction status will be imported."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; pakub GnuCashiga sarnast konto kooskõlastamise funktsiooni ning "
"imporditakse ka vastav tehingu olek."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commodities"
msgstr "Tooted"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:216
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "GnuCash uses the term Commodity to cover both currencies and non-currency "
#| "assets. These are treated separately in &kappname;."
msgid ""
"&gnucash; uses the term Commodity to cover both currencies and non-currency "
"assets. These are treated separately in &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"GnuCash kasutab mõistet \"tooted\" (Commodity) nii rahaliste kui ka "
"mitterahaliste varade kohta. &kappname; kohtleb neid eraldi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currencies"
msgstr "Vääringud"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:222
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; has built-in support for all foreign <link linkend=\"details."
#| "currencies\">currency</link> types. &kappname; also requires that the "
#| "user specify a base currency, this being the default currency for new "
#| "accounts. The importer will attempt to determine the most likely base "
#| "currency, though this choice may be rejected in favor of an alternative."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; has built-in support for all foreign <link linkend=\"details."
"currencies\">currency</link> types. &kmymoney; also requires that the user "
"specify a base currency, this being the default currency for new accounts. "
"The importer will attempt to determine the most likely base currency, though "
"this choice may be rejected in favor of an alternative."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;sse on sisse ehitatud kõigi välismaiste <link linkend=\"details."
"currencies\">vääringu</link>tüüpide toetus. Samuti nõuab &kappname;, et "
"kasutaja määraks baasvääringu, mis on kõigi uute kontode vaikimisi vääring. "
"Importija üritab kindlaks määrata kõige tõenäolisema baasvääringu, kuigi "
"selle valiku võib mõnda alternatiivi eelistades ka tagasi lükata."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:231
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "(NOTE: &kappname; does not currently support accounts denominated in "
