msgid ""
"&kmymoney; does not currently support accounts denominated in 'defunct' "
"currencies, except those replaced by the Euro. At present, it will be "
"necessary to remove any such accounts from your &gnucash; file before "
"importing. We hope to improve on this situation in a future release."
msgstr ""
"(MÄRKUS: &kappname; ei toeta praegu kontosid, mille vääringuks on mõni "
"\"kadunud\" vääring (välja arvatud need, mis on asendunud euroga). Praegu on "
"vajalik eemaldada sellised kontod GnuCashi failist enne importimist. Me "
"loodame olukorda parandada mõnes lähituleviku väljalaskes.)"

