msgstr "Ajaplaani tüübid"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:328
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; classifies all schedules as one of three types, Bills, "
#| "Deposits, or Transfers. Since GnuCash does not make such a distinction, "
