#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decoding Options"
msgstr "Dekodeerimisvalikud"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:414
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If your native language is written in letters or symbols which are "
#| "different from those used in the 'Latin' languages (i.e., generally "
#| "Western European), these are represented in a special fashion ('encoded') "
#| "in your GnuCash file. If these letters are not displayed correctly on "
#| "your screen, then they must be decoded. Currently, it is often not "
#| "possible to detect accurately which form of decoding must be used, so you "
#| "may need to set this option and select an entry from the list. In "
#| "general, the first item in the list will be that which is considered "
#| "appropriate for your locale (i.e., the country and language which was "
#| "selected as native when your operating system was installed), so this "
#| "should be tried first. Since the import process does not overwrite your "
#| "GnuCash file, you are free to experiment with any of these selections."
msgid ""
"If your native language is written in letters or symbols which are different "
"from those used in the 'Latin' languages (&ie;, generally Western European,) "
"these are represented in a special fashion (<quote>encoded</quote>) in your "
"&gnucash; file. If these characters are not displayed correctly on your "
"screen, then they must be decoded. Currently, it is often not possible to "
"detect accurately which form of decoding must be used, so you may need to "
"set this option manually by selecting an entry from the list. In general, "
"the first item in the list will be that which is considered appropriate for "
"your locale (&ie;, the country and language which was selected as native "
"when your operating system was installed,) so this should be tried first. "
"Since the import process does not overwrite your &gnucash; file, you are "
"free to experiment with any of these selections."
msgstr ""
"Kui sinu keeles kasutatakse tähti või sümboleid, mis erinevad nõndanimetatud "
"\"ladina\" keeltest (s.t. levinud Lääne-Euroopa keeltes kasutatavatest "
"märkidest), siis tähistatakse (\"kodeeritakse\") neid GnuCashi failis "
"erilisel viisil. Kui sa ei näe neid tähti oma ekraanil korrektselt, tuleb "
"need dekodeerida. Praegu ei ole sageli võimalik täpselt tuvastada, millist "
"dekodeeringut kasutada, mistõttu võib olla vajalik märkida see valik ja "
"määrata loendist vajalik kirje. Üldiselt on loendi esimene kirje see, mida "
"peetakse sinu lokaadi (s.t. riigi ja keele kombinatsiooni puhul, mis on "
"valitud juba operatsioonisüteemi paigaldamise ajal) puhul kõige sobivamaks. "
"Kuna importimisel ei kirjutata GnuCashi faili üle, võib siinsete valikutega "
"vabalt eksperimenteerida."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transaction Notes option"
msgstr "Tehingu märkuste valik"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:430
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Under some usage conditions, non-split GnuCash transactions may contain "
#| "residual, often incorrect, memo data which is not normally visible to the "
#| "user. When imported into &kappname; however, due to display differences, "
#| "this data can become visible. Often, these transactions will have a Notes "
#| "field describing the real purpose of the transaction. If this option is "
#| "selected, these notes, if present, will be used to override the "
#| "extraneous memo data."
msgid ""
"Under some usage conditions, non-split &gnucash; transactions may contain "
"residual, often incorrect, memo data which is not normally visible to the "
"user. When imported into &kmymoney; however, due to display differences, "
"this data can become visible. Often, these transactions will have a Notes "
"field describing the real purpose of the transaction. If this option is "
"selected, these notes, if present, will be used to override the extraneous "
"memo data."
msgstr ""
"Mõningate kasutustingimuste korral võivad tükeldamata GnuCashi tehingud "
"sisaldada sinna jäänud, sageli ebakorrektseid, memoandmeid, mida kasutaja "
"tavaliselt ei näe. &kappname;sse importimisel muutuvad need aga kuvamise "
"eripärade tõttu nähtavaks. Sageli on sellistel tehingutel väli Notes, mis "
"kirjeldab tehingu tegelikku eesmärki. Siinse valiku märkimisel kasutatakse "
"neid märkmeid, kui neid peaks olema, tarbetute memoandmete ülekirjutamiseks."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Debug Options"
msgstr "Silumisvalikud"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:441
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "These need only be used in the event of import problems. If you have such "
#| "problems, you should also report them to the &kappname; developer list "
#| "&devlist;. Note that the traces produced by these options may contain "
#| "data of a confidential nature, and the Anonymize option should be used if "
#| "they are to be made publicly available."
msgid ""
"These need only be used in the event of import problems. If you have such "
"problems, you should also report them to the developers' mailing list "
"&devlist;. Note that the traces produced by these options may contain data "
"of a confidential nature, and the <guilabel>Anonymize data</guilabel> option "
"should be used if they are to be made publicly available."
msgstr ""
"Neid läheb vaja ainult impordiprobleemide tekkimisel. Kui satud selliste "
"probleemidega silmitsi, peaksid neist teada andma ka &kappname; arendajate "
"postiloendissse &devlist;. Pane tähele, et nende valikutega loodud "
"tagasijälitus võib sisaldada konfidentsiaalset laadi andmeid, mistõttu enne "
"nende avalikuks tegemist peaks kasutama andmete anonüümseks muutmise "
"võimalust."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
